28","n4333"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AB%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%B7%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make someone/something lag behind"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to discourage","examples":[{"text":"يَا رَبِّ، خَلَقْتَنِي وَأَمَرْتَنِي، وَنَهَيْتَنِي وَرَغَّبْتَنِي فِي ثَوَابِ مَا أَمَرْتَنِي بِهِ[…]وَسَلَّطْتَ عَلَيَّ عَدُوًّا، فَأَسْكَنْتَهُ صَدْرِي، وَأَسْكَنْتَهُ مَجْرَى دَمِي، إِنْ أَهُمَّ بِفَاحِشَةٍ شَجَّعَنِي ، وَإِنْ أَهُمَّ بِطَاعَةٍ ثَبَّطَنِي، لَا يَغْفُلُ إِنْ غَفَلْتُ!"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to inhibit (of a drug)"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/θab.ba.tˤa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n4328","headword_ar":"ثَبِطَ","root":"vbT","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", [inf. n., accord. to rule,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaboTN","text_ar":"ثَبْطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] (K,) or, as Sgh says, [judging from the part. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vabiTN","text_ar":"ثَبِطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] thus analogy requires that it should be, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, stupid in his work,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"action; and weak:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man, and a horse, K and TA, said of a horse with respect to covering,"},{"kind":"page_break","n":331},{"kind":"text","text":"TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, heavy, sluggish,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slow."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA.)       -A2-  See also 2, in two places."}],"source_refs":["K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n4333","headword_ar":"ثَبِطٌ","root":"vbT","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Stupid in his work,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","t